---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import me from "../assets/images/me.png";
---

<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-text">
        <h1>Why?</h1>
        <div>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Eius dolorem optio sed explicabo laboriosam est eum eligendi minus cupiditate quo veritatis asperiores adipisci et voluptas quod, architecto cumque qui amet dignissimos, fugiat fugit fuga accusantium. Ratione, amet maxime, consequatur similique, a dolorem maiores quidem commodi officiis itaque atque temporibus tempore.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-image">
        <Image src={me} alt="text" id={"me-image"}/>
    </div>
</section>
    
<style>
    section.hero {
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        height: 80vh;
    }

    section.hero > div.hero-text {
        max-width: 50vw;
        margin: 0 4rem 0 auto;
    }
    section.hero > div.hero-image {
        width: 50vw;
    }
    .hero-text p {
        max-width: 45ch;
    }
    .hero-image > #me-image {
        object-fit: cover;
        width: 40%;
        height: auto;
        overflow-x: hidden;
    }
</style>